3
00:01:35,470 --> 00:01:36,555
L-ai găsit?

4
00:01:38,056 --> 00:01:39,141
E bine?

5
00:01:41,768 --> 00:01:43,103
Ce? Ce s-a întâmplat?

6
00:01:59,578 --> 00:02:01,413
Doamne, Leighton.

7
00:02:10,923 --> 00:02:11,924
La dracu '!

8
